### 🧠 Check if server is running
GET http://localhost:4000/

### 🎟️ Get all events
GET http://localhost:4000/events

### 🔍 Search events by keyword
GET http://localhost:4000/events?q=tech

### 🎯 Filter by category
GET http://localhost:4000/events?category=Technology

### 📅 Filter by date range
GET http://localhost:4000/events?dateFrom=2025-10-10&dateTo=2025-10-30

### 🗓️ Save an event to calendar
POST http://localhost:4000/calendar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": 1,
  "user": "student01"
}

### 🗓️ Get all calendar entries
GET http://localhost:4000/calendar

### 🎫 Claim a ticket and generate QR code
POST http://localhost:4000/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": 1,
  "user": "student01"
}
